com.google.code.ssm.api

Annotation Type ReturnValueKeyProvider


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface ReturnValueKeyProvider
    Marks the return value of method as a generator for cache keys. If any of the method in return object is marked with CacheKeyMethod then this method is used to generate cache key otherwise toString() method is used.
    Author:
    Nelson Carpentier
